2. An article of manufacture in accordance with claim 1, wherein said medium is a removable medium selected from the group consisting of: 
a compact disk (CD); 
a digital versatile disk (DVD); 
a magneto-optical (MO) disk; 
a magnetic tape; 
a magnetic disk; 
